The '''Nessarch''' was the elected mayor of the city of [[Yhaunn]] in [[Sembia]].
document_data.Activities: The position of Nessarch was chosen by the ruling [[Fives Council]] of Yhaunn. Once selected, a Nessarch would serve for life.
